Problem Statement: Write Code which will be able to operation of Find and replace, Complete Sentence or Paragraph can be given as input. You are allowed to use string.h library functions.

Sample I/p: 
1.
 Enter Input: Hi everyone hope so everyone is fine 
 What to Find: everyone
 Replace with: all

2.
 Enter Input: Hi my name is vinit
What to Find: it
Replace With: ay

3.
Enter Input: Hi my name is vinit and vinit lives in pune
What to Find: vinit
Replace With: vinitA

Sample O/p:
1. Hi all hope so all is fine 
2. Hi my name is vinay
3. Hi my name is vinitA and vinitA lives in pune